    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>窥视 | Peeping</strong>​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>一场理智与疯狂的监狱生存实验</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras/fe02412209cc43c5b996a0959a77d19e.avif?t=1771927720\" width=1438 height=810 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏简介</strong>​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《窥视》是一款以心理生存为核心的叙事解谜游戏。你扮演一名疑似拥有“偷窥”能力的主角，被关押在秘密监狱中接受为期31天的观察。你必须遵守严苛的作息表、躲避狱警的随机巡查，并悄悄使用那日渐侵蚀理智的能力——否则，你将因能力反噬而死去。但若滥用能力，又会被判定为“异常”，永远失去自由……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心玩法</strong>​</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存与伪装</strong>：在固定作息时间内完成指定动作，避免嫌疑值过高；在随机巡查中保持“正常”，一旦被发现异常行为，调查将提前结束。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras/eef5eb0e8ac4151be3c273b7956a0b8c.avif?t=1771927720\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras_big/eef5eb0e8ac4151be3c273b7956a0b8c.avif?t=1771927720 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力的代价</strong>：每3天必须使用一次“偷窥”能力维持生命，但每次使用都会加深被能力控制的风险。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>意识潜入</strong>：将意识化为“额外之眼”，窥视其他牢房，通过检查、分析、探索收集线索，拼凑隐藏的故事与监狱真相。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras/b4d51381ab325a3f1b818689758640a3.avif?t=1771927720\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras_big/b4d51381ab325a3f1b818689758640a3.avif?t=1771927720 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>监狱探索：</strong>获取狱警行动讯息后，可安排时间进行监狱潜行，获得游戏主线线索，了解这一场社会灾难背后的故事<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras/db763bbf5dcf76bd97efbe7c32ffe49d.avif?t=1771927720\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras_big/db763bbf5dcf76bd97efbe7c32ffe49d.avif?t=1771927720 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多重结局</strong>：你的每个选择将导向三种结局——死亡、被送入研究所，或是“通过测试”回归社会……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras/67872f31d33c6c578812c37cd464ccaa.avif?t=1771927720\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304430/extras_big/67872f31d33c6c578812c37cd464ccaa.avif?t=1771927720 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong>​</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>紧张的时间管理</strong>：在固定作息与随机巡查的夹缝中寻找“偷窥”的机会。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>递进的心理压迫</strong>：能力如毒瘾般侵蚀理智，不用则死，滥用则疯。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>碎片化叙事</strong>：通过窥视他人生活，逐渐揭开监狱的黑暗秘密与能力的恐怖真相。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极简交互与沉浸氛围</strong>：以第一人称视角与牢房环境互动，音效与光影烘托出孤寂与诡谲感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>警告</strong>​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每一次“窥视”，都在将自己推向失控的边缘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在31天后，以“正常人”的身份走出这里吗？</p>",
